                                confisicated by the end of the war, the were kept and indexed in Russian in the Lenin Library in <placeName
                                    ref="#l0439">Moscow</placeName>. In <date when-iso="1958">1958</date> the papers were returned to the <orgName
                                    ref="#stabi.berlin">Staatsbibliothek zu Berlin - Preußischer Kulturbesitz</orgName>.</p>
                            <p xml:lang="fr">Les papiers <persName ref="#p0237">Adelbert de Chamisso</persName> (NL 152) ont été acquis en <date
